# Content Rules

## Structure

- `content/worlds/` — World metadata, level lists
- `content/algorithm/` — Algorithmic thinking levels
- `content/chess/` — Chess levels
- `content/unplugged/` — Unplugged coding levels

## Rules

- Every level must conform to `@cognitive/content-schema` LevelSchema.
- No logic in JSON — only data (config, puzzle state, solution).
- Use semantic IDs: `algorithm/level-001`, `chess/level-010`.

## Level Fields (minimal)

Each level defines: `skill_target`, `difficulty`, `learning_goal`, `expected_behavior`.
